title: Intel Foundry customers call 14A "the real deal"
description: Patrick Moorhead of Moor Insights & Strategy has spoken to some Intel 14A customers. They view the node positively and are confident in its ability to be competitive.
content: Veteran analyst Patrick Moorhead has shared some new information about Intel's upcoming 14A node. Clients who have seen it say, "14A is the real deal", and it is highly competitive in key markets suc… [+1093 chars]
